title: 1am In Midtown Pt. I with Adam Pally and Dan Levy
description:
Live from The Four Seasons, Jimmy and Larry are joined by the Hollywood Jewish elite power duo of Adam Pally and Dan Levy, the star and creator of the upcoming NBC sitcom, “Indebted”. The boyz link up with their close, personal celebrity friends to learn wardrobe budget finessing 101, ranking Green Day’s best albums, punching Baby Yoda in the face, LA’s hottest fashion trends and much more in part 1 of a delirious, sleep-deprived edition of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
